Package it.polimi.ingsw.am43.Network.Messages.toClientMessages

Class availablePlacementsMsg

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am43.Network.Message
it.polimi.ingsw.am43.Network.Messages.toClientMessages.availablePlacementsMsg
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class availablePlacementsMsg extends Message
This message is sent from the server to the client during the player's turn. It contains all the corners of a card on which a placement is possible, as well as two booleans stating if the Resource and Gold decks are empty or not.
